      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   w-cod-mne-dcf-ope      .
           move      rr-cod-fnt           to   w-cod-mne-dcf-cod      .
           move      05                   to   w-cod-mne-dcf-lin      .
           move      30                   to   w-cod-mne-dcf-pos      .
           move      05                   to   w-cod-mne-dcf-rln      .
           move      41                   to   w-cod-mne-dcf-rps      .
